'''''Potomanto''''' (yakomotse ku ijambo ry'igifaransa ''portmanteau'' ) ni filime yo muri [[Gana|Gana ya]] 2013 - [[Nijeriya]] yerekana ibikorwa bya Shirley Frimpong Manso . Irimo Olu Jacobs, Yvonne Okoro na Adjetey Anang .  Yerekanwe bwa mbere muri Sinema ya Silverbird, [[Accra]], muri [[Gana]], ku ya 20 Ukuboza 2013.  

== Umugambi ==
Uwahoze ari umupolisi urakaye, Andane, akazi ke ni ugukora iperereza no gufata abafatanyabikorwa bahemutse afata indi sura iyo yahawe akazi ko gukora iperereza ku mugore wâ€™umucuruzi ukize. Yatsitaye ku mpeta y'abasaruzi b'ingingo n'abacuruzi bashuka abasore babasezeranya kubajyana mu mahanga. Umukwe wumukire numukozi wihishe nawe ukora iperereza kugirango afate abacuruza urugingo. Bishyize hamwe bagerageza guhagarika kanseri yatwaye ubuzima bwa benshi mu rubyiruko mu baturage. 

